            laboriosam ab ipsa molestiae reiciendis delectus, commodi natus
            adipisci sequi vel? Ipsam.
          </p>
          <button
            class='rounded-full bg-p300 px-4 py-2 font-bold text-white hover:bg-p500'
          >
            Buy Now
          </button>
        </Fragment>
      </GridContainer>
      <GridContainer direction='lg:flex-row'>
        <Fragment slot='section-1'>
          <Image src={book_dorian_gray} alt='WDL Logo' class='h-96 w-auto' />
        </Fragment>
        <Fragment slot='section-2'>
